divs: Sighting Detailsin my mother-in-laws driveway smoking, looked up, saw three orangish lights trailing one another, not a straight flight path, slightly wavering, going relativly slow, then go straight up into cloud cover, then about 15 seconds later a forth one followed the same path and went up in the same area as the first three
